"The problem is that there are still many Colombians whose data are not recorded anywhere", said CTI expert.
He explained that not everything is as it turns out in the CSI TV program.
Like everything that sparkles, there's no gold, not everything you touch, there's traces.
However, if it can be used, an appropriate comparison must be made.
